Hello! Thanks for visiting my profile  I've been a Turo Power Host for several years as a hobby/side business.

My cars are well maintained and my goal is to provide you the best Turo experience possible. 

Renting from me is pretty easy. Just follow the rules and if you have any requests, etc...just let me know.  If you need a vehicle earlier that your scheduled time etc just let me know and I will do what I can to make it happen. 

You will not have to deal with automated email responses and will not have to worry about getting in touch with someone in case you need anything on your rental. You will not get passed on to another person or receive any excuses.. Your vehicle will be washed, vacuumed, sanitized and ready to go when your rental begins. 

I offer contactless delivery for all of my rentals; so it's as easy as checking into your reservation and accessing the vehicle via the TuroGo app for all of my Tesla vehicles.  

Thanks for looking!!

D&R's AutoBaum, LLC is owned & managed by friends/entrepreneurs Dwayne Saunders & Rob Nussbaum (D & R) in Austin, TX.   We're "car lovers" from birth.  We promise to work tirelessly to give you a CLEAN, QUALITY vehicle & Turo experience.  To do so, we have the assistance of the entire auto mechanic & support team from Genuine Automotive & Diesel (owned by Dwayne) to ensure our vehicles are in TIP TOP mechanical & working order for our valued Turo guests!  We host the vehicles from the GA&D shop for constant attention to every detail.  Thanks in advance for renting with us!
